Details About the Electric Power System
* Underground power line from the KSEB.
* Three RMU units to divide the electricity to the three plants.

## * Plant 1 
* Three HT panels divide the power to Five different transformers.
* The power from the transformers it taken to the MV panel.
* There are 9 MV panels and each MV panles have a capacitor panel.
* The capacitor panel is used to remove harmonic from the A\C current and to have a contant capacitive load.
* The MV panel have a KSEB connection and a coupled diesel generator.
* There are 7 diesel generator.
* The MV panels are sub divide to power specific part of the plant
